Subject: drm/i915: Avoid endless HPD poll detect loop via runtime
 suspend/resume
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: cc018c2626745d2e52273f941f9db222101aa11a
